14 WHEREAS, throughout her tenure, she has played a vital role in promoting senior wellness
15 by developing and expanding health and fitness programs, encouraging healthy living, and
16 fostering an environment where seniors feel empowered to prioritize their well-being; and
17 WHEREAS, Joy Walston has established a glowing reputation of renown throughout Clayton
18 County, Georgia, for her dedication, leadership, and unwavering commitment to enriching
19 the lives of seniors; and
20 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
21 extraordinary servant leader be appropriately recognized.
22 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
23 the members of this body congratulate and commend Joy Walston for receiving the 2025
24 Yellow Rose Nikki T. Randall Servant Leadership Award and extend best wishes for her
25 continued success.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
27 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Joy
28 Walston.
